<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

  <title>BLOGO</title>
</head>

<body id="app">
  <!-- navbar -->
  <div class="container">
    <header class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center py-3 mb-4 border-bottom">
      <a href="#" class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3 mb-md-0 me-md-auto link-body-emphasis text-decoration-none">
        <img src="/Logo1.png" alt="logo-brand" height="30px">
      </a>

      <ul class="nav nav-pills">
        <li class="nav-item"><a href="/submit" class="btn btn-dark rounded-pill p-2 px-3" aria-current="page">Home</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a href="/write" class="nav-link">Write</a></li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a href="/" class="nav-link">LogOut</a></li>

      </ul>
    </header>
  </div>

  <!-- slider -->
  <div id="carouselExampleAutoplaying" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img src="/s1.png" class="d-block" alt="Welcome-image">
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img src="/s3.png" class="d-block" alt="Why">
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img src="/s2.png" class="d-block" alt="Made-By-Sameen">
      </div>
    </div>
    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleAutoplaying"
      data-bs-slide="prev">
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
    </button>
    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleAutoplaying"
      data-bs-slide="next">
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
    </button>
  </div>

  <!-- feature -->
  <div class="container px-4 py-5" id="hanging-icons">
    <h2 class="pb-2 border-bottom">What We Provide?</h2>
    <div class="row g-4 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3">
      <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
        <div
          class="icon-square text-body-emphasis bg-body-secondary d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-4 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="30" height="30" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-1-square-fill"
            viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path
              d="M2 0a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2zm7.283 4.002V12H7.971V5.338h-.065L6.072 6.656V5.385l1.899-1.383z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Create</h3>
          <p>Unlock your creativity with our intuitive creation tools. Whether you're crafting a blog post, designing a
            website, or composing a piece of music, our platform empowers you to bring your ideas to life with ease.
            From customizable templates to seamless collaboration features, we provide everything you need to unleash
            your imagination and transform your vision into reality.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
        <div
          class="icon-square text-body-emphasis bg-body-secondary d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-4 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="30" height="30" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-2-square-fill"
            viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path
              d="M2 0a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2zm4.646 6.24v.07H5.375v-.064c0-1.213.879-2.402 2.637-2.402 1.582 0 2.613.949 2.613 2.215 0 1.002-.6 1.667-1.287 2.43l-.096.107-1.974 2.22v.077h3.498V12H5.422v-.832l2.97-3.293c.434-.475.903-1.008.903-1.705 0-.744-.557-1.236-1.313-1.236-.843 0-1.336.615-1.336 1.306" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Add</h3>
          <p>Enhance your projects with a diverse array of multimedia elements. From stunning images and captivating
            videos to interactive maps and dynamic charts, our platform offers a wide range of tools to enrich your
            content and engage your audience. With just a few clicks, you can seamlessly integrate multimedia elements
            into your work and elevate its impact.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
        <div
          class="icon-square text-body-emphasis bg-body-secondary d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-4 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="30" height="30" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-3-square-fill"
            viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path
              d="M2 0a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2zm5.918 8.414h-.879V7.342h.838c.78 0 1.348-.522 1.342-1.237 0-.709-.563-1.195-1.348-1.195-.79 0-1.312.498-1.348 1.055H5.275c.036-1.137.95-2.115 2.625-2.121 1.594-.012 2.608.885 2.637 2.062.023 1.137-.885 1.776-1.482 1.875v.07c.703.07 1.71.64 1.734 1.917.024 1.459-1.277 2.396-2.93 2.396-1.705 0-2.707-.967-2.754-2.144H6.33c.059.597.68 1.06 1.541 1.066.973.006 1.6-.563 1.588-1.354-.006-.779-.621-1.318-1.541-1.318" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Delete</h3>
          <p>Streamline your workflow with our efficient deletion tools. Whether you're removing outdated content,
            trimming unnecessary sections, or decluttering your workspace, our platform makes it easy to clean up your
            projects and focus on what matters most. With simple yet powerful deletion features, you can quickly
            declutter your projects and keep them organized for maximum efficiency.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- blog -->
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Your Blog Posts</h1>
    <hr>
    <div class="row">
      <% if (locals.t) { %>
        <% for (let i=0; i < locals.t.length; i++) { %>
          <div class="col-md-1">
            <div class="p-2">
              <a href="/<%= locals.t[i] %>" class="btn btn-dark mb-3 delete">
                <%= locals.t[i] %>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% } %>
            <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- footer -->
  <div class="container">
    <footer class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between align-items-center py-3 my-4 border-top">
      <p class="col-md-4 mb-0 text-body-secondary">Â© 2024 BLOGO!, Pak</p>

      <a href="/"
        class="col-md-4 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3 mb-md-0 me-md-auto link-body-emphasis text-decoration-none">
        <svg class="bi me-2" width="40" height="32">
          <use xlink:href="#bootstrap"></use>
        </svg>
      </a>

      <p class="nav col-md-4 justify-content-end">Owner Sameen Zaki</p>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</body>

</html>